# AWS S3 bucket Host Docker Website
1. pull Docker Image 
2. Run Docker Image 
3. docker ps
4. docker cp 01c0de97c48b:/usr/share/nginx/html "$HOME/Desktop/html_backup"
# Work AWS s3 Backet 
5. Create Backet 
6. upload folder and move all Files To Root 
7. Permision 
7. Remove Check mark Block all public access
8. add Bucket policy 
<pre>
{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Sid": "AllowPublicReadAccess",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Principal": "*",
      "Action": "s3:GetObject",
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::finchproject/*"
    }
  ]
}
</pre>
9. Properties section 
Static website hosting edit and add index.html
